<P>
Consolidated Freightways Inc.: The Menlo Park, Calif.-based transportation and 
delivery company said third-quarter earnings rose 11% to $8.2 million. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue was up 7.2% to a record $1.1 billion. The company said strong trucking 
business and smaller losses at its Emery Worldwide letter- and package-delivery 
subsidiary boosted results. 
</P>
