<TEXT>
<P>
Reebok International Ltd.: The footwear and apparel designer and marketer 
reported third-quarter earnings of $41 million, down 18% from a year ago. Sales 
totaled $589 million, up 12%. The Stoughton, Mass., firm attributed the results 
to lower U.S. sales of its Reebok brand footwear and higher advertising and 
promotional expenses. 
</P>
