<HEADLINE>
<P>
PRAGER ON ISRAELI-ARAB CONFLICT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Prager is mistaken in his belief that Arabs hate Israel because it is 
democratic or embodies Western values. 
</P>
<P>
Arabs hate Israel for what it really is, a virulent, aggressive, colonial 
outpost of U.S.-supported cowboys using every brutal means at its disposal to 
oppress the indigenous Arab population. Even the U.S. wouldn't care if Israel 
was democratic or embodied Western values so long as Israel served our 
interests. Unfortunately, Prager's effort to gain the moral high ground for 
Israel is simply a rhetorical device to demonize Arabs among Americans. 
</P>
<P>
SHANT AGAJANIAN, Newport Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
