baseball team for the 1992 Summer Olympics at Barcelona, Spain. His U.S. 
assistants will be: Dave Snow, Cal State Long Beach coach; Brad Kelley, a Miami 
assistant, and Jerry Weinstein, a Sacramento City College coach. 
</P>
