<TEXT>
<P>
Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak arrived Monday on an unscheduled visit to 
Saudi Arabia to inspect Egyptian troops stationed in the northeast area near 
the Saudi-Kuwaiti border, officials said. Mubarak is also expected to confer 
with King Fahd. 
