Peru Looking for Buyers for State Airline: Peru, seeking private capital for 
money-losing state firms, has begun talks with U.S. and European airlines with 
the aim of selling off part of state-owned carrier AeroPeru, the airline's 
president has said. AeroPeru President Rodolfo Elmore said that Pan Am, 
