<P>
Cine-Source Stock: An Oct. 16 article incorrectly reported that the stock of 
Burbank-based Cine-Source Inc., co-producer of the movie "Texasville," fell 
from $6 a share on Oct. 7 to 21.875 cents a share on Oct. 15. 
</P>
<P>
